      "docs": {
        "markdown": "# SortableList\n\n| | |\n|---|---|\n| **Category** | `Components` |\n| **Tags** | `sortable` `list` `a11y` |\n| **Variants** | 4 |\n\n## Variants\n\n### Setlist `default`\n\n```vue\n<p class=\"hint\">Drag rows, or focus one — <kbd>Space</kbd>, arrows, <kbd>Space</kbd>.</p>\n<SortableList\n  class=\"setlist\"\n  :items=\"setlist\"\n  :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n  @update:items=\"(next) => (setlist = next)\"\n>\n  <template #item=\"{ item, index }\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"order\">{{ index + 1 }}</span>\n    <span class=\"name\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n    <span class=\"time\">{{ item.length }}</span>\n  </template>\n</SortableList>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Springy neighbors\n\n```vue\n<p class=\"hint\">\n  The same list with <code>styles/spring.css</code> physics, scoped to this subtree.\n</p>\n<SortableList\n  class=\"setlist springy\"\n  :items=\"springy\"\n  :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n  @update:items=\"(next) => (springy = next)\"\n>\n  <template #item=\"{ item, index }\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"order\">{{ index + 1 }}</span>\n    <span class=\"name\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n    <span class=\"time\">{{ item.length }}</span>\n  </template>\n</SortableList>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Two independent lists\n\n```vue\n<div class=\"days\">\n  <section>\n    <h3 class=\"day\">Saturday</h3>\n    <SortableList\n      class=\"setlist\"\n      :items=\"saturday\"\n      :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n      @update:items=\"(next) => (saturday = next)\"\n    >\n      <template #item=\"{ item }\">\n        <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n        <span class=\"name\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n      </template>\n    </SortableList>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n    <h3 class=\"day\">Sunday</h3>\n    <SortableList\n      class=\"setlist\"\n      :items=\"sunday\"\n      :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n      @update:items=\"(next) => (sunday = next)\"\n    >\n      <template #item=\"{ item }\">\n        <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n        <span class=\"name\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n      </template>\n    </SortableList>\n  </section>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Horizontal\n\n```vue\n<SortableList\n  class=\"stops\"\n  orientation=\"horizontal\"\n  :items=\"stops\"\n  :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n  @update:items=\"(next) => (stops = next)\"\n>\n  <template #item=\"{ item }\">\n    <span class=\"name\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n  </template>\n</SortableList>\n```\n\n---\n\n## Source\n\n```\n../src/sortable/SortableList.vue\n```\n\n",
